Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:10.09,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.26,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在由心发出呐喊时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:16.72,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:19.77,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:28.07,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}对自己坦率些最好
